  "body": "`scrollLeft` and `scrollTop` are specified in HTMLDOMPropertyConfig, I understand what they're probably for. But what is the use-case? Doesn't it make more sense to just let users set/update them manually (on DOM nodes)?\n\nI'm asking because we currently emit invalid attributes for them, we also don't set the properties when reusing server-markup, so they seem really really hacky right now.\n\ncc @zpao @spicyj @yungsters \n",
